| Mode | What runs |
|------|-----------|
| `quick` | build + ctest + health check |
| `standard` | quick + API smoke + IPC smoke |
| `strict` | standard + parity checks + planning brief validation + `gh status` |
| `screenshot` | quick + TUI screenshot capture for visual review |

Default: `quick`

